							<li class="flip" id="flip_2_1">Use energy monitoring and management hardware and
								software <span class="checkmark" id="2_1"></span>
								<div class="panel" id="panel_2_1">
									To understand how to change something, it is essential to assess it first. List of energy
									management software for organization may vary from open source to commercial fully
									supported products. <br>Reference - <a
										href="http://www.capterra.com/energy-management-software/">Energy management software</a>
